# Placeholder for Screenshots

This directory will contain promotional screenshots for extensions.gnome.org submission.

Required screenshots (3-5 PNG files):
1. screenshot-menu.png - Main menu display
2. screenshot-model-breakdown.png - Per-model breakdown
3. screenshot-idle-notification.png - Idle detection warning
4. screenshot-preferences.png - Preferences window
5. screenshot-cost-tracking.png - Cost tracking (optional)

See README.md in this directory for detailed instructions on creating screenshots.

These screenshots must be created on a GNOME system with the extension installed.
